                        <p>Semaglutide reduced cardiovascular events by 20% in non-diabetic patients. GLP-1 medications show promise beyond weight management.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="science-card animate-on-scroll animate-delay-3">
                        <h3>ITP Studies</h3>
                        <p>Rapamycin has extended lifespan in mammalian studies. Research continues into its effects on cellular aging pathways.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
